ỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%A9-Kh%C3%B4ng-Linh-ng%E1%BA%A1n/poem-WcCIPCyQSdOHHb7bX3XTZQ">Thứ Không Linh ngạn - 次空靈岸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/Tr%E1%BB%AB-d%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-c%C6%B0/poem-0WtRbum6ARHtUv2ph-FqYw">Trừ dạ tân cư - 除夜新居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/author-sRemHKkmYCdxkkHc58hcHA">Cừu Viễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%C3%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81u-hoa/poem-BSa2eOwq-xO46rUlIZrKzA">Vãn thiều hoa - 晚韶華</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-ch%C6%B0-nhi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-azhgRihjoDlmY3BTEHnfpg">Xuân nhật thị chư nhi kỳ 2 - 春日示諸兒其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
